    "how_it_works_4dPttU": {
      "type": "how-it-works",
      "blocks": {
        "accordion_xTqqU8": {
          "type": "accordion",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Technical specifications",
            "text": "<p><strong>TREATMENT TIME: </strong>3 minutes</p><p><strong>CERTIFICATES: </strong>FDA, TGA, CE, UKCA</p><p><strong>OPERATION: </strong>Wireless, hands-free</p><p><strong>WAVELENGTH: </strong>415nm (Blue), 605nm (Amber), 630nm (Red), 660nm (Deep Red), 880nm (Infrared)</p><p><strong>TREATMENT TIME: </strong>2 hours</p><p><strong>CHARGING TIME: </strong>3 minutes</p><p><strong>LEDs: </strong>160 dual core</p>"
          }
        },
        "accordion_tNf6Vj": {
          "type": "accordion",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Treatment details",
            "text": "<p><strong>USE: </strong>Use daily after cleansing, before topical skincare</p><p><strong>SKIN REJUVENATING TREATMENT: </strong>605nm (Amber), 630nm (Red), 660nm (Deep Red), 880nm (Infrared)</p><p><strong>SKIN CLEARING TREATMENT: </strong>415nm (Blue), 630nm (Red)</p><p><strong>CUSTOMIZED TREATMENT: </strong>Choose treatment modes for each facial area via app</p><p><strong>Skin Type: </strong>Suitable for all Fitzpatrick Skin Types I-IV</p>"
          }
        }
      },
      "block_order": [
        "accordion_xTqqU8",
        "accordion_tNf6Vj"
      ],
      "name": "t:sections.how-it-works.name",
      "settings": {
        "heading": "How it works",
        "text": "<p>The Q-Rejuvalight Pro LED mask uses 5 light wavelengths and two modes for customizable skincare. Our FDA-cleared device targets your skin's needs.</p>",
        "image_aging": "shopify://shop_images/mask_aging.webp",
        "image_breakout": "shopify://shop_images/mask_breakout.webp",
        "heading_aging_mode": "<p><strong>Skin Rejuvenating</strong></p>",
        "text_aging_mode": "<p>On Skin Rejuvenating Mode, red and infrared wavelengths work together to help improve the appearance of skin texture and firmness. <br/><br/>Red light helps improve the look of skin smoothness and radiance. Deep red and infrared light work at different depths of the skin’s surface to help improve the look of wrinkles over time.</p>",
        "heading_breakout_mode": "<p><strong>Skin Clearing</strong></p>",
        "text_breakout_mode": "<p>Our Skin Clearing Mode combines blue and red light wavelengths. Blue (415 nm) targets the bacteria associated with mild-to-moderate acne, while red (630 nm) helps calm and soothe the appearance of irritated skin.<br/><br/>Together, these wavelengths help improve the appearance of breakouts, support clearer-looking skin, and promote a balanced, healthier-looking complexion.</p>"
      }
    },
