          "settings": {
            "heading": "How often can I use the treatment?",
            "text": "<p>You can use the mask daily. In fact, consistent daily use is recommended for best results. <br/><br/>Each session takes just 3 minutes, and the more regularly you use it, the more noticeable the improvements in skin tone, texture, and clarity over time.</p>",
